They finally got the sub into the cave and started for the opening 
into the underground river.

Stallex: Mutate can you fly?

Mutate: Yes.

Stallex: None of us can and who knows when our friend will get back. I 
was getting mixed signals from the southern tip of this contienent. 
Looks like there might be a battle down there. At least one faction'll 
probably be friendly. You should go see if they'll tell you what's 
going on on this planet.

Mutate: O.k.. I'll be back soon.

He flies off toward Maximal city.
